WEBVTT

00:10:28.400 --> 00:10:30.376
"The Black Hills are not for sale."

00:10:31.630 --> 00:10:32.789
2010:

00:10:33.329 --> 00:10:36.121
Statistics about Native population today,

00:10:36.145 --> 00:10:39.376
more than a century
after the massacre at Wounded Knee,

00:10:39.400 --> 00:10:41.985
reveal the legacy of colonization,

00:10:42.009 --> 00:10:43.277
forced migration

00:10:43.301 --> 00:10:44.744
and treaty violations.

00:10:45.895 --> 00:10:48.325
Unemployment on the Pine Ridge
Indian Reservation

00:10:48.349 --> 00:10:50.927
fluctuates between 85 and 90 percent.

00:10:51.689 --> 00:10:54.538
The housing office is unable
to build new structures,

00:10:54.562 --> 00:10:56.698
and existing structures are falling apart.

00:10:57.030 --> 00:10:58.199
Many are homeless,

00:10:58.223 --> 00:11:00.782
and those with homes
are packed into rotting buildings